AWS DynamoDB is a fast and flexible NoSQL database service
Fully managed NoSQL database suitable for document & key-value store models
Stored on SSD Storage
High availability since it is spread across 3 geographically distinct data centres
Suitable for read heavy applications rather than heavy write applications
Offers Two Read Consistency Types:
  -> Eventually consistent reads
  -> Strongly consistent reads
Writing to DynamoDB is expensive
Reading from Dynamo is cheap
